[pengerusi Persatuan Kebajikan Hospital Kiang Wu
,]

00:42:27.840 --> 00:42:28.550
??? Aku berkongsi kesedihanmu, aku berkongsi kemarahanmu ???

00:42:28.550 --> 00:42:29.490
[Majlis Eksekutif Macau,]

